    "headline": "Molson Coors Beverage Company Announces Proposed Public Offering of United States Dollar-Denominated Senior Notes",
    "summary": "GOLDEN, Colo. & MONTREAL, May 20, 2026--Molson Coors Beverage Company (\"MCBC,\" \"Molson Coors\" or \"the Company\") (NYSE: TAP, TAP.A, TAP 32; TSX: TPX.A, TPX.B) announced today that it has commenced an underwritten public offering (the \"Offering\") of U.S. dollar-denominated senior notes (the \"Notes\"). The Offering is expected to close on or about May 27, 2026, subject to customary closing conditions.",
